      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About| the visual condition}}
{{Infobox disease
| Name           = Blindness
| ICD10          = {{ICD10|H|54|0|h|53}}, {{ICD10|H|54|1|h|53}}, {{ICD10|H|54|4|h|53}}
| ICD9           = {{ICD9|369}}
| Image          = Long cane.jpg
