| [[Commonwealth Day]]
| Celebrated nationwide as the Queen's birthday. National Sports Council holds horse races in Belize City at the National Stadium and in [[Orange Walk Town]] at the People's Stadium. Cycle races are held between Cayo and Belmopan. The three-day Toledo Cacao Festival is held in the [[Toledo District]] over the Commonwealth Day Holiday Weekend.
