rect 98 206 117 224 [[Plateau Department|Plateau]]
rect 62 211 78 229 [[Zou Department|Zou]]
&lt;/imagemap&gt;
{{Main|Departments of Benin|Communes of Benin}}
Benin is divided into 12 [[department (subnational entity)|departments]] (French: ''départements''), and subdivided into 77 [[commune (subnational entity)|commune]]s. In 1999, the previous six departments were each split into two halves, forming the current 12. The six new departments have not been assigned an official capital yet.{{Verify source|date=July 2009}}

